---
title: Mozz-Stuffed Caprese Burgers with Griddled Tomato, Creamy Pesto & Potato Wedges
description: Meet Caprese salad—burger-fied! Yep, our chefs transformed everyone’s favorite Italian appetizer into a dinner-worthy burger. And no, they didn’t just combine the two by stacking tomato, mozzarella, and basil on top of a plain ol’ patty—they took it to a whole new level. Think Italian-seasoned beef patties stuffed with melty mozz, then topped with griddled tomato slices and a creamy pesto sauce. Everything is tucked into toasted buns and served with a heap of crispy potato wedges on the side. Buon appetito!
